Make better than zapier

Tools You Should Prioritize for Your Agency
Make – For general workflow automation with advanced logic and integrations.
Botpress – For custom conversational AI and chatbot development.
Stack AI – For AI-driven workflows, predictive analytics, and machine learning-based automation.
OpenAI API – For GPT-powered automation (e.g., automating content generation, chatbots).
Google Cloud AI or Azure AI – For more advanced machine learning models, if your clients require custom AI solutions.
